Note: Rethgaard, mentioned on the signs in this area, is a stone fortress on or near Ruathym originally built by seagoing dwarves (according to WotC's 'The North'). It was plundered during the war between Luskan & Ruathym. The text is a bit confusing about who it sided with, though I think it was Luskan. Now it serves as the War Knight keep.
